name: ProjectX
description: ProjectX is a BEP-20 token, created to push the boundaries of the crypto sphere to a different level by creating a higher standard. The token includes within it a set of utilities and features: X-Club - inhouse staking. X-Productions - Movie productions. NFT Collections - will be integrated to our game. X-Giving - Donations. X-Starter - Start-up Platform. P2E-Game - Xcape.
